presets.Add.description:
PRESETS [Client] Adds preset to a preset group.

[string] groupname
  The preset group name, usually it's tool class name.

[string] name
  Preset name, must be unique.

[table] values
  A table of preset console commands.

presets.Exists.description:
PRESETS [Client] Returns whether a preset with given name exists or not

[string] type
  The preset group name, usually it's tool class name.

[string] name
  Name of the preset to test

presets.Remove.description:
PRESETS [Client] 

[string] groupname
  Preset group to remove from

[string] name
  Name of preset to remove

presets.Rename.description:
PRESETS [Client] Renames preset.

[string] groupname
  Preset group name

[string] oldname
  Old preset name

[string] newname
  New preset name
